<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Body>
    <Title>新冠确诊数呈指数级增长，南非反驳英国“甩锅”言论</Title>
    <ReportTime type="absTime">2020-12-26T00:00</ReportTime>环球时报
    <Content>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>自
                <Event eid="e1">
                    <Denoter did="d1" type="operation">发现</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o1" type="recipient">变异新冠病毒</Object>
                </Event>后，
                <Event eid="e2">
                    <Object oid="o2" type="recipient">南非</Object>再度遭受
                    <Object sid="s2" type="agent">疫情</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d2" type="operation">冲击</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e3">
                    <Object sid="s3" type="agent">新增确诊病例</Object>
                    <Means mid="m3" type="method">呈指数级</Means>
                    <Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">增长</Denoter>
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e4">
                    <Time tid="t4" type="relTime">24日</Time>，
                    <Location lid="l4">南非</Location>
                    <Denoter did="d4" type="operation">新增</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o4" type="recipient">新冠肺炎确诊病例14305例</Object>
                </Event>，超过周三的14046例，连续两日
                <Event eid="e5">
                    <Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">打破</Denoter>南非3月暴发新冠肺炎疫情后
                    <Object oid="o5" type="recipient">单日新增确诊病例纪录</Object>
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。
            <Sentence>本月1日，南非新增确诊病例仅为2295例</Sentence>。
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e6">据
                    <Participant sid="s6" type="agent">路透社</Participant>
                    <Time tid="t6" type="relTime">25日</Time>
                    <Denoter did="d6" type="statement">报道</Denoter>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e7">
                    <Participant sid="s7" type="agent">南非卫生部长穆凯兹</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d7" type="statement">表示</Denoter>
                </Event>，第二波新冠肺炎疫情的传播比第一波更快，
                <Event eid="e8">确诊病例正
                    <Means mid="m8" type="method">呈指数级</Means>
                    <Denoter did="d8" type="stateChange">增长</Denoter>
                </Event>，这很可能是
                <Event eid="e9">由
                    <Object sid="s9" type="agent">变异的新冠病毒</Object>
                    <Denoter did="d9" type="stateChange">导致</Denoter>
                </Event>
            </Sentence>。
            <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e10">
                    <Participant sid="s10" type="agent">他</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d10" type="statement">说</Denoter>
                </Event>，“
                <Event eid="e11">
                    <Participant sid="s11" type="agent">我们</Participant>
                    <Denoter did="d11" type="operation">敦促</Denoter>
                    <Participant oid="o11" type="recipient">所有南非人</Participant>
                </Event>
                <Event eid="e12">
                    <Denoter did="d12" type="operation">遵守</Denoter>与国家灾难状态有关的
                    <Object oid="o12" type="recipient">法规和建议</Object>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e13">
                    <Denoter did="d13" type="operation">避免</Denoter>
                    <Object oid="o13" type="recipient">大型集会</Object>和
                    <Object oid="o13" type="recipient">拥挤的环境</Object>
                </Event>，
                <Event eid="e14">
                    <Denoter did="d14" type="operation">确保</Denoter>
                    <Location lid="l14" type="destination">人员聚集的地点</Location>有
                    <Object oid="o14" type="recipient">足够的通风</Object>
                    </Event>，并
                    <Event eid="e15">
                        <Denoter did="d15" type="operation">保持</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o15" type="recipient">警惕</Object>
                    </Event>，
                    <Event eid="e16">
                        <Denoter did="d16" type="operation">遵守</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o16" type="recipient">干预措施</Object>
                    </Event>。”
                </Sentence>
                <Sentence>
                    <Event eid="e17">
                        <Time tid="t17" type="relTime">目前</Time>，
                        <Location lid="l17">南非</Location>仍
                        <Denoter did="d17" type="operation">维持</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o17" type="recipient">一级封锁措施</Object>（最高五级）
                    </Event>，
                    <Event eid="e18">
                        <Participant sid="s18" type="agent">南非卫生部</Participant>
                        <Time tid="t18" type="relTime">24日</Time>
                        <Denoter did="d18" type="statement">表示</Denoter>
                    </Event>，
                    <Event eid="e19">将重新
                        <Denoter did="d19" type="operation">审定</Denoter>
                    </Event>
                    <Event eid="e20">
                        <Denoter did="d20" type="operation">调整</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o20" type="recipient">防疫措施</Object>
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
                <Sentence>
                    <Event eid="e21">截至
                        <Time tid="t21" type="relTime">25日</Time>，已有
                        <Object sid="s21" type="agent">14个国家或地区</Object>
                        <Denoter did="d21" type="stateChange">暂停</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o21" type="recipient">往来南非航班</Object>
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Sentence>
                    <Event eid="e22">
                        <Location lid="l22">英国</Location>与
                        <Location lid="l22">南非</Location>先后
                        <Denoter did="d22" type="operation">发现</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o22" type="recipient">变异新冠病毒</Object>
                    </Event>，但对于病毒的传染力和起源，
                    <Event eid="e23">
                        <Participant sid="s23" type="agent">两国卫生部门</Participant>
                        <Denoter did="d23" type="operation">打</Denoter>起了
                        <Object oid="o23" type="recipient">嘴仗</Object>
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
                <Sentence>
                    <Event eid="e24">据
                        <Object sid="s24" type="agent">“南非人”新闻网</Object>
                        <Time tid="t24" type="relTime">25日</Time>
                        <Denoter did="d24" type="statement">报道</Denoter>
                    </Event>，
                    <Event eid="e25">
                        <Participant sid="s25" type="agent">穆凯兹</Participant>
                        <Time tid="t25" type="relTime">24日</Time>
                        <Denoter did="d25" type="statement">发表</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o25" type="recipient">声明</Object>
                    </Event>
                    <Event eid="e26">
                        <Denoter did="d26" type="operation">反驳</Denoter>了
                        <Object oid="o26" type="recipient">英国卫生大臣汉考克的指责</Object>
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
                <Sentence>穆凯兹在声明中称：“
                    <Event eid="e27">
                        <Participant sid="s27" type="agent">汉考克</Participant>
                        <Time tid="t27" type="relTime">近日</Time>
                        <Denoter did="d27" type="statement">表示</Denoter>
                    </Event>，英国变异病毒感染病例均与南非到访人士相关，
                    <Event eid="e28">
                        <Denoter did="d28" type="statement">暗示</Denoter>
                    </Event>
                    <Event eid="e29">
                        <Object sid="s29" type="agent">南非发现的变异病毒</Object>在英国第二波疫情中
                        <Denoter did="d29" type="operation">扮演</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o29" type="recipient">主要角色</Object>
                    </Event>，这是不正确的
                </Sentence>。
                <Sentence>
                    <Event eid="e30">有
                        <Object sid="s30" type="agent">证据</Object>
                        <Denoter did="d30" type="statement">表明</Denoter>
                    </Event>，
                    <Event eid="e31">
                        <Object oid="o31" type="recipient">英国病毒变种</Object>
                        <Denoter did="d31" type="operation">发现</Denoter>得更早
                    </Event>，可
                    <Event eid="e32">
                        <Denoter did="d32" type="operation">追溯</Denoter>到
                        <Time tid="t32" type="absTime">今年9月20日</Time>
                    </Event>，约比南非变种出现的时间早一个月
                </Sentence>。”
                <Sentence>此外声明指出，
                    <Event eid="e33">
                        <Time tid="t33" type="relTime">目前</Time>没有
                        <Object sid="s33" type="agent">证据</Object>
                        <Denoter did="d33" type="statement">表明</Denoter>南非变种比英国变种更具传染性或导致更高的死亡率
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
                <Sentence>
                    <Event eid="e34">
                        <Object sid="s34">现有的疫苗是否能抵御这些病毒变种</Object>还需要
                        <Denoter did="d34">研究</Denoter>
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Sentence>另据中国驻南非大使馆网站25日消息，
                    <Event eid="e35">
                        <Time tid="t35" type="relTime">近日</Time>在
                        <Location lid="l35">南非</Location>
                        <Object sid="s35" type="agent">中国公民感染新冠肺炎病例</Object>呈现快速
                        <Denoter did="d35" type="stateChange">上升</Denoter>势头
                    </Event>，导致
                    <Event eid="e36">新增
                        <Participant sid="s36" type="agent">2人</Participant>
                        <Denoter did="d36" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter>
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
                <Sentence>
                    <Event eid="e37">
                        <Location lid="l37">约翰内斯堡唐人街</Location>
                        <Denoter did="d37" type="operation">发生</Denoter>
                        <Object oid="o37" type="recipient">聚集性感染事件</Object>
                    </Event>，已有
                    <Event eid="e38">
                        <Participant sid="s38" type="agent">多人</Participant>
                        <Denoter did="d38" type="operation">确诊</Denoter>
                    </Event>
                </Sentence>。
            </Paragraph>
        </Content>
